title: Stunning 3-Bedroom in Kilimani
description: Experience urban living at its finest in this spacious 3-bedroom apartment located in the heart of Kilimani. Featuring modern finishes, a fully equipped kitchen, and a balcony with city views. The complex includes a swimming pool, gym, and 24/7 security. Perfect for families or professionals.

title: Luxurious 5-Bedroom Villa in Karen
description: An exquisite 5-bedroom family home in the serene neighborhood of Karen. This property boasts a large mature garden, private swimming pool, and a spacious outdoor entertainment area. All bedrooms are en-suite, with a large master suite featuring a walk-in closet and private balcony.

title: Modern 2-Bed with City Views
description: A chic and modern 2-bedroom apartment in Westlands with breathtaking views of the Nairobi skyline. This unit is perfect for young professionals, offering easy access to shopping malls, restaurants, and offices. Residents enjoy access to a rooftop pool and lounge.

title: Cozy Townhouse in a Gated Community
description: Charming 4-bedroom townhouse in a secure gated community in Lavington. This home features a private garden, ample living space, and modern kitchen. It's an ideal choice for families looking for a safe and quiet environment.

title: Elegant Condo in Kileleshwa
description: Discover this elegant 3-bedroom condo in the prestigious Kileleshwa neighborhood. With high-end finishes, an open-plan living area, and large windows offering plenty of natural light, this property is the epitome of comfort and style.
